{"type":"text","timestamp":1775840896748,"sessionID":"ses_287a39e14ffexmWh3KcsbEq6fe","part":{"id":"prt_d785d6897001Cc9mAo2zQVLnF0","messageID":"msg_d785d6044001kQgomZLsq6QoSz","sessionID":"ses_287a39e14ffexmWh3KcsbEq6fe","type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete picture. Let me produce the verification report:\n\n## Verification Report: AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量\n\n### Summary\n\n**Status: ❌ NOT IMPLEMENTED**\n\nThe spec describes a full client-go library with typed clients, informers, listers, and fake clients. **None of this generated code exists in the codebase.**\n\n---\n\n### Detailed Findings\n\n#### 1. pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 — ✅ EXISTS (Partial)\n\n**Implemented:**\n- ✅ `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList` CRD types\n- ✅ Shared types: `ResourceQuota`, `NetworkPolicy`, `NetworkRule`, `LifecycleHook`, `ContainerSpec`\n- ✅ `AgentRuntimeCondition` pattern for status reporting\n- ✅ `CodeInterpreterSpec` (as sub-spec, NOT a separate CRD)\n- ✅ Scheme registration (`register.go`)\n- ✅ Deepcopy generation (`zz_generated.deepcopy.go`)\n- ✅ Validation functions\n- ✅ Defaulting functions\n\n**Missing:**\n- ❌ **`CodeInterpreter` CRD type** — Spec requires separate `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types with `+genclient` marker for client-go generation\n\n---\n\n#### 2. client-go library — ❌ NOT GENERATED\n\n**Entire directory missing:**\n```\nclient-go/\n├── clientset/versioned/\n│   ├── clientset.go          ❌ MISSING\n│   ├── scheme/               ❌ MISSING\n│   ├── fake/                 ❌ MISSING\n│   └── typed/runtime/v1alpha1/\n│       ├── runtime_client.go ❌ MISSING\n│       ├── agentruntime.go   ❌ MISSING\n│       ├── codeinterpreter.go ❌ MISSING (requires CodeInterpreter CRD)\n│       └── fake/             ❌ MISSING\n├── informers/externalversions/ ❌ MISSING\n└── listers/runtime/v1alpha1/   ❌ MISSING\n```\n\n**Required interfaces per spec:**\n- ❌ `Interface` / `Clientset` with `RuntimeV1alpha1()` accessor\n- ❌ `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` with `AgentRuntimesGetter` + `CodeInterpretersGetter`\n- ❌ `AgentRuntimeInterface` (CRUD methods)\n- ❌ `CodeInterpreterInterface` (CRUD methods) — **Cannot exist without CodeInterpreter CRD**\n- ❌ `SharedInformerFactory`\n- ❌ `AgentRuntimeLister` / `CodeInterpreterLister`\n\n---\n\n#### 3. Root Cause\n\n**Spec-Code Mismatch:**\nThe spec assumes `CodeInterpreter` is a **separate CRD** (lines 68-70 of client-go.md):\n> Same method shape as `AgentRuntimeInterface`, types `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter` / `CodeInterpreterList`\n\nBut in the implementation, `CodeInterpreterSpec` is only an **embedded sub-spec** within `AgentRuntimeSpec`.\n\n---\n\n### Required Actions\n\n1. **Add CodeInterpreter CRD** to `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`:\n   ```go\n   // +genclient\n   // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n   type CodeInterpreter struct { ... }\n   type CodeInterpreterList struct { ... }\n   ```\n\n2. **Update register.go** to register `CodeInterpreter` types\n\n3. **Run code generator**: `make gen-client` (invokes `hack/update-codegen.sh`)\n\n4. **Verify generated files** match spec:\n   - `clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n   - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n   - `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n   - `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n\n---\n\n### Tests\n\nNo tests can be verified because the client-go code doesn't exist. Once generated, tests should verify:\n- Typed client CRUD operations\n- Informer factory wiring\n- Lister functionality\n- Fake client behavior","time":{"start":1775840896744,"end":1775840896744}}}
